{"tid":2037161,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"傳騰訊將在北美成立 3A 工作室，前育碧製作人負責","createTime":"2020-05-27T00:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T04:48:15.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b611c0c30a9e4d63381886c90fb7c982d4adea6","tid":2037161,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:21:21.000Z","msg":"傳騰訊將在北美成立 3A 工作室，前育碧製作人負責<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/19121903/video-game-624x416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F19121903%2Fvideo-game-624x416.jpg&h=e75c642b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據資深遊戲製作人 Scott Warner 近期在 Twitter 訊息，騰訊或將在北美開設新的 3A 工作室，他將擔任負責人。<br />\n<br />\nScott Warner<br />\n@scottfeed<br />\nI am moving on to a new role. I&rsquo;ll be the studio director of a new AAA operation in North America for Tencent. We will be hiring for all disciplines at all levels so reach out to me for details.<br />\n上午10:38 &middot; 2020年5月16日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/19161206/2020-05-19_160704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F19161206%2F2020-05-19_160704.jpg&h=49bb8900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nScott Warner LinkedIn 資料顯示，他曾經在 343 工作室擔任設計總監參與《最後一戰 4》研發，後來加入 EA 成為製作人參與《戰地風雲：強硬路線》，以及幾個未公布的星球大戰專案研發；宣布加入騰訊前，他在育碧舊金山工作室擔任製作人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nScott Warner<br />\n@scottfeed<br />\nWe are still looking for an experienced multiplayer game designer to join our team here @UbisoftStudioSF <a href=\"https://jobs.smartrecruiters.com/Ubisoft2/743999711414073-senior-multiplayer-game-designer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjobs.smartrecruiters.com%2FUbisoft2%2F743999711414073-senior-multiplayer-game-designer&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=e63e83af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jobs.smartrecruiters.com/Ubisoft2/743999711414073-senior-multiplayer-game-designer</a> #ubisoft #gamejobs<br />\n<br />\n▲ Scott Warner 5 月在 Twitter 發表育碧徵才資訊。<br />\n<br />\n截至消息發表前，騰訊未回應此事。<br />\n<br />\n之前騰訊曾在北美設立波士頓工作室，後來不了了之，也未曾正式發表產品。2019 年 9 月，騰訊天美位於洛杉磯地區的工作室發出徵才啟事，尋求創意總監和製作人，要求應聘者需「3 年以上 3A 遊戲製作經驗」，另外「對寶可夢懷有了解和熱情是加分項」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/19161407/1589861587616778-e1589876053641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F19161407%2F1589861587616778-e1589876053641.jpg&h=ea11e6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近騰訊招聘公布的美國地區徵才資訊顯示，騰訊 Lightspeed Studio 和 Timi Studio 都在徵有 5~10 年工作經歷的資深遊戲人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/19161529/1589862059505395.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F19161529%2F1589862059505395.jpg&h=44204e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各種跡象表明，騰訊正在持續強化北美地區自研團隊實力，並可能已在嘗試製作 3A 等級的遊戲。這次籌備新 3A 工作室的傳聞，或許意味騰訊的 3A 遊戲產品布局，又向前邁進了一步。"},{"pid":"3d0f5ce819710b517268076f20f941770f6c4cf5","tid":2037161,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"準備抄隻pokemon出黎?"},{"pid":"0dbf6194c11d17d08fb60dc1bf4cd204899d6303","tid":2037161,"uid":283428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"共產小精靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0908ddc4d7803a756a17d24c943230f6e62e42d8","tid":2037161,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"山海經xi"},{"pid":"b78286d2dd4be5bc4cdacef3d577c46d587a583f","tid":2037161,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"整完當自己國家3a game"},{"pid":"3672400a89b33874ac75bc220ae2a1e48a63e762","tid":2037161,"uid":66274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T